  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this study is to verify the effectiveness of the new ACAP 速 Confirm
      algorithm in the automatic management of atrial capture.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
  <start_date>January 2014</start_date>
